{"tid":776911,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己嘅焦慮越嚟越嚴重","createTime":"2018-08-12T13:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T13:27:54.000Z","uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6816f9575e6b3599e7c01fcd8745e5c11b7f3b57","tid":776911,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"根本出到街見到人就好驚好炆<br />\n成日比老母逼出街個下真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢講我有幾咁驚，佢屌鳩返我要習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有抑鬱有焦慮 你估我想㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都有嘗試去控制自己<br />\n睇個醫生就係咁話貴，咁我咪唔睇唔book時間囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 病發又比你屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時想自己一個出去散心又屌我唔帶埋佢出去<br />\n我想要私人空間姐 有無咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a426c67a374dc8c1254f51e7b8eb8770ecc08650","tid":776911,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"我都盡量話佢知我唔開心啲咩，到頭來係話返我唔捱得又成<br />\n19歲人有咩唔係我自己捱過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都好大壓力，明明好比心機去讀書，考唔入個科就屌我無努力過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱確診有情緒病就鬧我係到玩乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我前排同佢講我想死，成家人就係到話我係到玩咩自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以重視下我嘅感受 好似無人明我有幾咁難受咁"},{"pid":"669373fbb4e713fa1fd925b7e6f49e299bc1bfbe","tid":776911,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T13:26:28.000Z","msg":"又唔好意思向朋友放負 講得多我都覺自己煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我越嚟越覺得活著比死更難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefaddb91f0fd0eaf8c2817f65fd46387eeee03f","tid":776911,"uid":15352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"咁咪上嚟呻吓 實有人會肯聽嘅"}]}